<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15344</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂和乔伊放学后飞快地回到家，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把自行车停在门廊边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爷爷！”她们大喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在这儿，后院。”她们听到他大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“走，凯蒂。”乔伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们朝后院跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷在盖一个有栅栏的鸡圈，地上放着一堆木头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊打开了鸡舍的门，六只鸡都跑了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，小鸡们！”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您知道吗？爷爷！”凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在是龙卷风季节，我们必须做好准备！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好主意。”爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是组长。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷扬起了眉毛。“小组？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多诺万龙卷风安全小组。”凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们今晚要开会。啊！我得去准备一下！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸下班回家时，乔伊还在鸡圈里转悠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，大家好，鸡圈真不错！”爸爸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂在家里忙什么呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，爸爸。”乔伊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，凯蒂正忙着当组长。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用鞋踢了踢那堆木头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爷爷，您打算怎么处理这些多余的木头？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道。”爷爷摸着下巴说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116821</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”爸爸说，“如果我八岁，我知道我会做什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116821</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会盖一座树屋。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“树屋？”乔伊说，“嗯......”她看了看爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您觉得我能盖一座树屋吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，当然了。”爸爸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只需要一点帮助，你就能做到。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们可以成为一个团队？”乔伊问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你需要一些结实的木板作地板。”爷爷说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以在回收中心弄些铁板作屋顶。” 爸爸补充道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊抱住了爸爸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这一定很有趣！”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要画一张我们树屋的画。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我已经可以想象得到了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚饭后，乔伊在客厅里画画。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爷爷坐在她对面，研究着他的园子计划。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们说要在春天看新出的橡树叶子。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当它们长到松鼠耳朵那么大的时候，就该种玉米了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185050</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你一直在给西瓜籽浇水吗，乔伊？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192758</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然了，爷爷。”乔伊笑着回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192758</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，凯蒂大步走进房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们开始开会吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她戴着一顶棒球帽，帽子前面写着“组长”。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“龙卷风季节到了！”她宣布道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多诺万龙卷风安全小组必须做好准备！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她低头看了看笔记本。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，我们要选择我们的避难所。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它应该在地下的某个地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223819</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想我们应该用地下室。”爷爷说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就像我们一直做的那样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好主意。”凯蒂说，“那很容易！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来，我们需要一个收音机和一个手电筒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来负责这些。”爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们还需要一个急救箱。”凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈，您能帮忙吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，组长。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妈妈。”凯蒂嘟哝说</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，我忍不住。”妈妈笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们还需要一些毯子和枕头。”凯蒂解释道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些我也会负责的。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有乔伊，我们需要瓶装水和零食。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278272</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280294</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好的，我现在就做。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>来吧，爸爸。该计划我们的树屋了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等一下。”凯蒂说，“这次会议还没有结束。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊坐了回去，转动着眼珠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂又开始指手画脚了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298372</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“树屋？”凯蒂想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把手放在额头上闭上了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有个好主意。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她一下子睁开了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的！”她喊道，“多诺万龙卷风安全小组需要一个树屋！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这会是一个气象观测站！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她转向乔伊。“盖一个！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊迅速向凯蒂敬礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是，组长！”她笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂有时可能很霸道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>334307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，她也很有趣！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>